		<p>Sidenote: My dad is experimenting with PIC controllers. He has a very simple program which simulates a Wake-up Light without sound. It seems to be simple (and cheap) to make these lights yourselves with the aid of a small backlit LCD, a dimmer, and a PIC controller (and some patience with a soldering iron).</p>

